name: U.S. Fuel Ethanol Industry Biorefineries and Production Capacity, USA, 1.15.2008
description: This dataset displays the cities in which the United States Ethanol BioRefineries Locations are located. Also included in this data is the name of the company and the feedstock information. Current capacity and changes due to expansion and under construction is included. This data was collected from the Renewable Fuels Association at: http://www.ethanolrfa.org/industry/locations/and was accessed on January 15, 2008.
